OL,3,CFootballer on his mission to help
OL,4,Cothers after death of his parents
OL,6,FA professional footballer who lost
OL,7,Fboth of his parents hopes that sharing
OL,8,Fhis experience will help others in a
OL,9,Fsimilar situation.
OL,11,FShortly before signing for Norwich
OL,12,FCity in October, Danish midfielder Emi
OL,13,FMarcondes, 29, was dealing with the
OL,14,Fdeath of his father, Kim, who passed
OL,15,Faway last summer.
OL,17,F12 years previous to that, his mum
OL,18,FMarilia died when Marcondes was just
OL,19,F17.
