OL,3,CFootballer on his mission to help
OL,4,Cothers after death of his parents
OL,6,F"But, I feel that I am strong enough
OL,7,Fnow to even lose the best friend I
OL,8,Fhad. It's still quite tough that's
OL,9,Fhe's not here though because he was
OL,10,Fthe person that I spoke to after
OL,11,Fgames."
OL,13,FAs a teenager, Marcondes initially
OL,14,Ffound it tough to deal with his
OL,15,Fmother's death.
OL,17,FHowever, he says he then "came to
OL,18,Fterms with it" as time progressed -
OL,19,Feventually dedicating a series of
OL,20,Ftattoos on his left-arm to her memory.
