OL,3,CFootballer on his mission to help
OL,4,Cothers after death of his parents
OL,6,F"I eventually forgave her. She loved
OL,7,Fus and she was a good person," he said.
OL,9,F"She tried to do everything she could
OL,10,Fand that was when I thought that she's
OL,11,Fstill given me life and she's done a
OL,12,Fgood job. That's when I thought that
OL,13,Fmy left-arm is going to be dedicated
OL,14,Fto her."
