OL,3,CFootballer on his mission to help
OL,4,Cothers after death of his parents
OL,6,FAccording to Child Bereavement UK, an
OL,7,Festimated 46,300 children under the
OL,8,Fage of 17 lose a parent every year -
OL,9,Faround 127 a day.
OL,11,FThe kind of shocking figures that
OL,12,Fprompted Marcondes to speak out
OL,13,Fpublicly, so that others know they're
OL,14,Fnot alone.
OL,16,F"If I can be open about it and help
OL,17,Fother people, that will make me
OL,18,Fhappy," he said.
